main event: Several people in Elkton, Kentucky saw a round, saucer-shaped object the size of a small automobile in the sky.
interesting points: The object was seen by multiple witnesses.
The object was described as saucer-shaped and the size of a small automobile.
The object was visible for around 15 minutes before disappearing.
The report categorizes the object as possibly being a military or civilian aircraft.
The official conclusion was that the object was possibly an aircraft.
